comment: Smith (NYK) and Payton (ORL) make incidental contact on the perimeter.
Galloway (ORL) goes under the screen set by Vucevic (ORL) and the two make incidental contact as Vucevic moves down the lane to get into rebounding position.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that the Hardaway (NYK) field goal was a 2 point basket was upheld.
Thomas (NYK) makes contact with Oladipo's (ORL) body and arm and the contact affects his movement to the basket and causes him to lose control of the ball.
Acy (NYK) sets the screen on Green (ORL) and gives him the opportunity to stop and/or change direction.
Vucevic (ORL) makes contact Hardaway Jr.'s (NYK) body and the contact affects his shot attempt.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that the ball was last touched by Thomas (NYK) was upheld and Orlando retained possession.
Vucevic (ORL) sets the screen on Thomas (NYK) and gives him the opportunity to stop and/or change direction.
Smith (NYK) makes incidental contact with Oladipo's (ORL) arm that does not affect his shot attempt.
Harris (ORL) makes contact with Galloway's (NYK) arm and body and the contact affects his movement to the basket and shot attempt prior to the contact near the restricted area with Gordon (ORL).
Vucevic (ORL) continues to move as he sets the screen on Galloway (NYK) without giving him the opportunity to stop and/or change direction.
Frye (ORL) gets his hands on the ball and forces the jump ball against Early (NYK).
Vucevic (ORL) sets the screen on Thomas (NYK) and gives him the opportunity to stop and/or change direction.
